Package: scpopulation
Title: Population Data and Projections for South Carolina Counties
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("N J", "Pinder", , "nicholas.pinder@des.sc.gov", role = c("aut")),
    person("C A", "Pellett", , "c.alex.pellett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Laljeet", "Sangha", , "lsangha@ucanr.edu", role = "ctb"),
    person("State of South Carolina Department of Environmental Services", role = "fnd")
  )
Maintainer: Nicholas Pinder <nicholas.pinder@des.sc.gov>
Description: Provides historical population data and future population projections 
    for South Carolina counties. Contains data from the SC Office of Revenue and 
    Fiscal Affairs (RFA), with extensions to 2070 and additional high-growth 
    scenarios. Includes tools for visualization and analysis of population trends.
